data.name: GDOGE Finance
data.description:
GDOGE is a deflationary cryptocurrency on the Binance Smart Chain.

Every transaction is taxed 5%, of which 2% is distributed to holders and 3% is locked in liquidity forever.

55% of the 1 trillion total supply was burned at launch.

Both the ownership of the contract and the LPs were burned.


Frictionless Yield Farming
Holders automatically receive 2% of all transactions without paying gas fees, risk of impermanent loss and providing token spending approval. Holding is farming.

More than Deflationary
55% to the total supply was burned at launch and it receives the major part of the 2% tax automatically burning more coins every transaction.

Ever Rising Price Floor
3% of all transactions are locked forever in liquidity, essentially burning more coins with each transaction and creating a rising price floor over time.

Un-Ruggable and 100% Community Owned
GDOGE was stealth launched with no team token allocation. The ownership of the contract was sent to the burn address, meaning no rug pull or coin minting are possible. The community is fully in charge.
